data.name: lbl_about.Text
data.value:
The Billiard Table Management System
is a simple application that allows user(s) to manage the billiard table. The system contains:
* Add Players to a Table - Each of the four [4] tables must contains TWO PLAYERS
* Remove Players from a Table - This function deletes players who are done and marks the table to "AVAILABLE"
* Display All Table and Availabillity - The user(s) can view all the tables with its current status. Either if it is "OCCUPIED" or "AVAILABLE"
* Update Player Payment/Bets - This allows updating each players payment or bets
